          "lord",
          "soldier"
        ],
        "IdentityIds": null,
        "IsFemale": null,
        "IsClanLeader": null,
        "SkillMin": null
      },
      "Content": "加里俄斯皇帝万万岁！他能带我们打胜仗，带我们分红，和我们同甘共苦，我们永远支持他！！拉盖娅和卢孔就是俩傻逼，哪有我们伟大的大统领好？A"
    },
    {
      "Priority": 0,
      "When": {
        "HeroIds": null,
        "Cultures": null,
        "KingdomIds": [
          "empire_s"
        ],
        "SettlementIds": null,
